{"tid":1568342,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"正確抵制藍商做法","createTime":"2019-09-14T09:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T08:24:38.000Z","uid":137789,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb2767890f7d40dbe2b51246ae4d5a1a8f97454","tid":1568342,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:21:11.000Z","msg":"集中集團，唔好全部係藍都抵制<br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解大家覺得黑警咁仆街？<br />\n<br />\n因為佢哋選擇性執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n選擇性抵制先係最毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「點解揀我噃」<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過黃店俾人搞都唔係間間出事<br />\n<br />\n呢啲就係寒蟬效應<br />\n<br />\n呢啲就係白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n以彼之道還施彼身<br />\n大家最痛恨唔係分化撚咩？<br />\n<br />\n如果分化撚係分化對家又如何？<br />\n<br />\n而且最重要其實係咁<br />\n<br />\n如果你全部都抵制<br />\n<br />\n個list又咁長<br />\n<br />\n執行起上嚟唔係咁易<br />\n<br />\n萬一搞唔起<br />\n<br />\n又或者持續唔到<br />\n<br />\n就好可惜<br />\n<br />\n唯有逐一擊破先係最有勝算"},{"pid":"16eca7e3453f54d6878bcee7cdd6bd4e91ea065c","tid":1568342,"uid":276716,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:26:02.000Z","msg":"不如每月票選最應該受制裁商家"},{"pid":"0d6cd4d6440d182bd50f9dcfa77836c92db9a0ef","tid":1568342,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:26:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c19a127bf746b9416ab6b87ab1864a75d5f539e5","tid":1568342,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16eca7e3453f54d6878bcee7cdd6bd4e91ea065c","tid":1568342,"uid":276716,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:26:02.000Z","msg":"不如每月票選最應該受制裁商家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:27:40.000Z","msg":"㩒錯咗負皮，sorry<br />\n我手動幫你正評翻"},{"pid":"da21a009e96fbae757d1c7d5333fcac406d00663","tid":1568342,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:27:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6cfcf1e5c183203232890a65e9d868e52fd3b0c6","tid":1568342,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db14855986393fd50fc3fba83c8b107bdef49862","tid":1568342,"uid":268712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:45:43.000Z","msg":"藍絲搞左一間紅油，<br />\n每次經過樓下間明星開的華星排晒隊，有幾多香港人死左<br />\n個D 人唔覺自已食更血咩<br />\n搵D 良心小店食堅持一下真係咁難"},{"pid":"556415fdb88a0280e5be8c2cd8609cea7d9ff47a","tid":1568342,"uid":276716,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:01:07.000Z","msg":"大範圍嘅抵制可以繼續做，但同時應有個每月焦點，集中打擊。<br />\n<br />\n如果只得大圍抵制，等如將打擊力量分散，由眾多商家分擔損失，對佢地其實影響有限。<br />\n<br />\n例如十間商家，每月每間損失10%生意，可能仲捱得住。但如果變成其中一間，嗰個月損失100%生意，咁就好可怕了"},{"pid":"e17a879215a66b10c7477b0d6f1f2b73248b7977","tid":1568342,"uid":137789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"556415fdb88a0280e5be8c2cd8609cea7d9ff47a","tid":1568342,"uid":276716,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:01:07.000Z","msg":"大範圍嘅抵制可以繼續做，但同時應有個每月焦點，集中打擊。<br />\n<br />\n如果只得大圍抵制，等如將打擊力量分散，由眾多商家分擔損失，對佢地其實影響有限。<br />\n<br />\n例如十間商家，每月每間損失10%生意，可能仲捱得住。但如果變成其中一間，嗰個月損失100%生意，咁就好可怕了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:08:42.000Z","msg":"一定係重點打擊，逐一擊破"},{"pid":"61624a4af27f85d613c0e5a6ca3fce835eefd2be","tid":1568342,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:36:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"49ccd19f7d90e5f617d90d0b82e69039977cc835","tid":1568342,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:39:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e94c5a6331062aa520f920db20c52bd795ce146d","tid":1568342,"uid":299694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:54:56.000Z","msg":"唔錯"},{"pid":"8ed5a5317bde820bd679734a795c3469bb6d2c27","tid":1568342,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply